OL,3,CPoliceman in fatal 999 crash found
OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA police officer who caused a fatal
OL,7,Fcollision with a 74-year-old woman on
OL,8,Fa motorbike while he answered a grade-
OL,9,Fone emergency call about a choking
OL,10,Fbaby has been convicted of causing
OL,11,Fdeath by dangerous driving.
OL,13,FPc Mark Roberts was speeding when he
OL,14,Fwent through a red light which had
OL,15,Fbeen on "stop" for six seconds and
OL,16,Fcollided with Ronald and Muriel
OL,17,FPinkney in his marked Northumbria
OL,18,FPolice Peugeot 308.
