OL,3,CPoliceman in fatal 999 crash found
OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FMrs Pinkney sustained fatal head and
OL,7,Fneck injuries in the collision on a
OL,8,F30mph stretch of road near the
OL,9,FMetrocentre in Gateshead in July 2022.
OL,11,FThe 57-year-old officer, who lives in
OL,12,FDarlington, had admitted causing death
OL,13,Fby careless driving but denied the
OL,14,Fmore serious offence of causing death
OL,15,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,17,FThe jury at Teesside Crown Court took
OL,18,F56 minutes to come to their verdicts
OL,19,Fon Wednesday (4 February).
