OL,3,CPoliceman in fatal 999 crash found
OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FThe Northumbria Police officer was
OL,7,Falso convicted of causing Mr Pinkney,
OL,8,Fwho suffered a bleed on the brain and
OL,9,Fmultiple fractures, serious injury by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving.
OL,12,FThe prosecution said Roberts should
OL,13,Fhave approached the junction more
OL,14,Fslowly and told the jury the police's
OL,15,Froadcraft guidance stated that risk
OL,16,Ftaking, even in a "noble cause", was
OL,17,Fnot justified.
OL,19,FJudge Francis Laird KC granted Roberts
OL,20,Fbail ahead of his sentencing on 7
OL,21,FApril.
