OL,6,FThe judge said: "The jury have
OL,7,Fconvicted you of the more serious
OL,8,Foffences and, with your background,
OL,9,Fyou understand the significance.
OL,11,F"I will need to consider what is an
OL,12,Fappropriate sentence for the two
OL,13,Foffences for which you have been found
OL,14,Fguilty and I will benefit greatly from
OL,15,Fa pre-sentence report."
