OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FRoberts, who has been suspended by his
OL,7,Fforce, was arrested after the
OL,8,Fcollision and later answered "no
OL,9,Fcomment" to questions during his
OL,10,Fformal interview but provided a
OL,11,Fprepared statement.
OL,13,FIn it, he said the ambulance service
OL,14,Fhad requested assistance about a
OL,15,Fchoking five-week-old baby, which
OL,16,Findicated paramedics did not believe
OL,17,Fthey could get to the patient before
OL,18,Fpolice.
