OL,3,CPoliceman in fatal 999 crash found
OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FRoberts said he took his marked
OL,7,Fvehicle from Whickham police station,
OL,8,Factivated his blue lights and sirens,
OL,9,Fchanging the tone of the alert at
OL,10,Ftimes, as he made his way through
OL,11,Ftraffic and red lights.
OL,13,FMoments before the collision with the
OL,14,FPinkneys' motorbike, the officer saw a
OL,15,Fwhite van make an emergency stop, he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"I couldn't see anything else before
OL,19,Ftravelling towards the junction," the
OL,20,Fofficer said in his statement, which
OL,21,Fwas read out in court on Tuesday.
