OL,6,F"The next thing I recall is there was
OL,7,Fa bang and both airbags deployed and I
OL,8,Fhit the windscreen, which knocked me
OL,9,Fout for a few seconds."
OL,11,FHe then saw two people on the ground
OL,12,Fwith crash helmets on.
OL,14,FHe blacked out again and was treated
OL,15,Fin an ambulance and then taken to
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,18,FHe finished his statement by offering
OL,19,FMrs Pinkney's family his "sincere
OL,20,Fcondolences".
