OL,3,CPoliceman in fatal 999 crash found
OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FMr Pinkney, now 81, was interviewed by
OL,7,Fpolice and said he could hear a police
OL,8,Fsiren but it seemed to be coming from
OL,9,Fa long way away.
OL,11,FMr Pinkney said: "I had not seen the
OL,12,Fpolice car driven by Pc Mark Roberts
OL,13,Fbefore the collision."
OL,15,FSumming up the case, the judge told
OL,16,Fjurors it would be understandable if
OL,17,Fthey held sympathy for the Pinkneys or
OL,18,Fthe defendant, describing him as "a
OL,19,Fserving police officer responding to
OL,20,Fan emergency and who, of course, never
OL,21,Fintended to cause anyone any harm".
