OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FDawn Hunter, the daughter of Mr and
OL,7,FMrs Pinkney, said after the verdict:
OL,8,F"It was an accident, I think he was
OL,9,Fguilty of careless but not dangerous
OL,10,F(driving) and I don't want him to go
OL,11,Fto prison.
OL,13,F"It's taken a long time to get over,
OL,14,FI'm still not over it. I don't think I
OL,15,Fever will be, but we're getting there
OL,16,Fas a family."
OL,26,@rD@ApmrD@Ipn
