OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FAfter the case, Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable Andy Hill said: "I'm fully
OL,8,Faware that no words will make the pain
OL,9,Fof Mr Pinkney, his family and anyone
OL,10,Fimpacted by this tragic incident, any
OL,11,Feasier.
OL,13,F"On behalf of Northumbria Police, I
OL,14,Fwish to express my sincere condolences
OL,15,Ffor your loss."
OL,17,FMr Hill said the case was referred to
OL,18,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct, who carried out an
OL,20,Finvestigation and a file was sent to
OL,21,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service.
