OL,4,Cguilty of death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FRoberts will now face a misconduct
OL,7,Fhearing.
OL,9,FMr Hill said: "Each and every day we
OL,10,Frespond to emergencies and thankfully
OL,11,Ftragedies of this nature are extremely
OL,12,Frare.
OL,14,F"Officers are highly-trained and
OL,15,Fsupported to help ensure they keep
OL,16,Fboth themselves and the public safe.
OL,18,F"Regrettably, on this occasion the
OL,19,Fstandard of driving fell short of what
OL,20,Fit is expected which has led to the
OL,21,Fmost devastating of outcomes."
